gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 128, Pacers 116
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic scored a new season high 128 points and defeated the Pacers, 128-116. Paolo Banchero recorded a game high 24 points to go along with three rebounds and two blocks for the Magic, Franz Wanger added 19 points and seven rebounds in the victory. Jordan Nwora tallied 19 points and five rebounds for the Pacers in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 8-5 in the regular season, while the Pacers fall to 7-5.
